snippet.title: Manafinder Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1582410/Manafinder 

Take the role of a manafinder in this Japanese-style turn-based RPG set in the beautiful but unforgiving world of Aevi. Fight your way against ferocious beasts and other threats in the quest for manastones as you define the fate of the exiled. 

Manafinder is in development for PC coming out in 2022!

Learn more at https://manafinder.com

Follow us on our social media channels! https://linktr.ee/manafinder
